OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,FThe BBC should clearly set out how it
OL,7,Fplans to attract younger viewers as it
OL,8,Ffaces "intense competition for
OL,9,Fattention" from other media providers,
OL,10,Fa parliamentary report has warned.
OL,12,FThe Public Accounts Committee (PAC)
OL,13,Fsaid the BBC's mission to "serve all
OL,14,Faudiences" is at risk as younger age
OL,15,Fgroups view content elsewhere while it
OL,16,Fsaid the corporation's digital first
OL,17,Fstrategy could risk older or less
OL,18,Fdigitally connected audiences being
OL,19,Fleft behind.
