OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,FThe publishing of the report on Friday
OL,7,Fcomes as the BBC has been hit by a
OL,8,Fseries of scandals in recent months,
OL,9,Fleading up to the resignation of
OL,10,Fdirector-general Sir Tim Davie, who
OL,11,Fgave evidence to the PAC for the
OL,12,Freport.
OL,14,FPAC chairman Conservative MP Sir
OL,15,FGeoffrey Clifton-Brown described the
OL,16,FBBC as "an organisation under severe
OL,17,Fpressure".
OL,26,@xD@HOUyD@IO]
