OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,FAmong several findings, the report
OL,7,Fsaid the BBC is not doing enough to
OL,8,Fenforce collection of the licence fee,
OL,9,Fwhich it described as unfair to the
OL,10,Fvast majority of households who do pay
OL,11,Ffor a licence.
OL,13,FIt said licence fee evasion and
OL,14,Fhouseholds not purchasing a licence
OL,15,Ftogether represented more than #1.1
OL,16,Fbillion in potential lost income in
OL,17,F2024/25.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
