OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,FIt also said the BBC had missed
OL,7,Fopportunities to save money and
OL,8,Fimprove customer engagement by not
OL,9,Fdigitising the licence fee, and
OL,10,Frecommended it now do so.
OL,12,FThe PAC also highlighted how the BBC
OL,13,Fdoes not provide clear information
OL,14,Fabout its commercial investments,
OL,15,Ftargets and actual returns from its
OL,16,Fcommercial activities, and said it
OL,17,Fshould begin to provide annual reports
OL,18,Fon this.
