OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,FIssues with regional services were
OL,7,Falso cause for concern and it said the
OL,8,FBBC should clearly communicate how it
OL,9,Fwill ensure better representation of
OL,10,Flocal communities "to sustain trust
OL,11,Fand relevance in the future".
OL,13,FIt said PAC members were "concerned
OL,14,Fthat decisions labelled as 'local',
OL,15,Fsuch as moving operations to
OL,16,FManchester or Birmingham, risk
OL,17,Foverlooking the identity and needs of
OL,18,Fsmaller communities".
OL,26,@rD@SOUsD@\O]uD@ZOUzD@TO]
