OL,6,FReforms such as the restructuring of
OL,7,Fregional news hubs and changes to the
OL,8,Flocal democracy reporting service "may
OL,9,Fhave unintentionally diluted the BBC's
OL,10,Fconnection with the communities it
OL,11,Faims to serve", it added.
OL,13,FIt also highlighted how the BBC is
OL,14,Fbehind target in developing new
OL,15,Fintellectual property (IP), "which in
OL,16,Fturn will limit sustainable long-term
OL,17,Frevenue streams".
OL,26,@pD@cOUsD@NO]wD@]OUyD@PO]
