OL,6,FNaming children's TV series Bluey as
OL,7,Fan example of "the commercial value
OL,8,Fthis can bring", it said the BBC
OL,9,Fshould set out how it will prioritise
OL,10,Fgenerating new IP.
OL,12,FThe report said the BBC's mission to
OL,13,F"serve all audiences" is at risk, with
OL,14,Fjust 51% of younger people feeling the
OL,15,FBBC reflects them, while their overall
OL,16,Fuse of BBC services ` including TV,
OL,17,Fradio or online ` is significantly
OL,18,Flower than other age groups.
OL,26,@oD@OOUpD@OO]uD@AOUuD@UO]
