OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,F"With audiences now able to access an
OL,7,Funprecedented range of content from a
OL,8,Fvariety of providers, the BBC faces
OL,9,Fintense competition for attention",
OL,10,Fthe report said.
OL,12,F"Its digital-first strategy is an
OL,13,Fimportant response and there are
OL,14,Fpromising signs of innovation, such as
OL,15,Fusing platforms like TikTok to share
OL,16,Fnews content with new demographics.
OL,18,F"However, this shift also carries a
OL,19,Frisk: those without reliable digital
OL,20,Faccess could find themselves excluded
OL,21,Ffrom core BBC services."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@bO]tD@AOUzD@AOU}D@XO]
