OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,FThe report said the BBC should now set
OL,7,Fout how it will ensure access and
OL,8,Fengagement with all audiences,
OL,9,Fincluding innovation in digital access.
OL,11,FSir Geoffrey said: "The BBC is an
OL,12,Forganisation under severe pressure.
OL,14,F"Its own founding aspiration to be a
OL,15,Ftruly universal broadcaster reflecting
OL,16,Fall its viewers means that this
OL,17,Fpressure, from both within and
OL,18,Fwithout, is inherent in its mission.
OL,26,@sD@TOUvD@AOU
