OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,F"Our report offers a snapshot of the
OL,7,FBBC's efforts to deliver value for
OL,8,Fmoney as it seeks to thrive in an
OL,9,Fincreasingly fragmented media
OL,10,Flandscape and illustrates the tensions
OL,11,Fit must navigate in multiple areas of
OL,12,Fits business ` in efficiently
OL,13,Fcollecting the licence fee; in
OL,14,Fproviding that universal service; in
OL,15,Fstaying relevant to its audiences.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
