OL,3,CBBC an 'organisation under severe
OL,4,Cpressure' ` report
OL,6,F"On the licence fee, our report makes
OL,7,Fclear that the ground is shifting
OL,8,Fbeneath the BBC's feet ` the
OL,9,Ftraditional enforcement method of
OL,10,Fhousehold visits is seeing fewer and
OL,11,Ffewer returns at a time of heightened
OL,12,Fcompetition for almost every aspect of
OL,13,Fthe BBC's activities.
OL,15,F"Our report shows that without a
OL,16,Fmodernised approach focused more on
OL,17,Fonline viewing, the broadcaster will
OL,18,Fsee faith in the licence fee system
OL,19,Febb away.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
