OL,6,F"Similarly, while efforts to
OL,7,Fdistribute itself more equitably
OL,8,Facross the nation are welcome in
OL,9,Fprinciple, the BBC must ensure that
OL,10,Fgreater distribution does not equal
OL,11,Fgreater dilution of the authentic
OL,12,Flocal quality of its coverage."
